00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
The system assigns default profile pictures
based on the name's first letter.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
However, users with the same letter
will have different colors or images.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
This allows for easy differentiation of
authors, even if they share an initial.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:18.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
Visual identity remains unique for
each account within the platform.